data.description: Welcome home to the gated community of Arden Hood Condominiums! Townhouse style! This welcoming and cozy downstairs unit features approximately 1,200 square feet, two bedrooms with walk-in closets, and two bathrooms. The living room is complete with a wood-burning fireplace. Enjoy the eat-in kitchen with beautiful granite countertops and a skylight to bring in natural light. Located just off the kitchen is the private patio where you can relax and entertain. Additional features include vaulted ceilings in the primary bedroom and lots of closet and storage space. The complex has two swimming pools and beautiful trees that give this community a park-like feel. Centrally located close to freeways and retail shopping and moments to Arden Fair Mall and Arden Arcade Area and CAL Expo. Home is no longer staged!
